If you’re dreaming of refreshing Getaway let me show you some awesome places around Switzerland 🇨🇭 🍃

When it comes to traveling are you more of a nature person or a city person 🤔

𝐁𝐞𝐚𝐮𝐭𝐢𝐟𝐮𝐥 𝐒𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐳𝐞𝐫𝐥𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐃𝐞𝐬𝐭𝐢𝐧𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐬
📍Switzerland 🇨🇭
1. @jo0sef Graubünden 
2. @emrije.a Foroglio Ticino 
3. @sennarelax Arolla 
5. @doounias Melchsee-Frutt
6. @wolfgangsiess Niederhorn
7. @_ahtravel_ Grindelwald
8. @syifa_in_switzerland Gimmelwald
9. @samuel_keller_1970 Äescher
10. @life_of_fab27 Lake Klontal

Say hello To Rasta the adventurous White Shepherd 🐶 😍

Here are some videos from Bernese Oberland and some other places in Canton Bern 🇨🇭

Did you visited any of these places if yes From 1-10 which place did you visit share you experiences with us 🍃

📍Switzerland 🇨🇭
📸 @rastawhiteshepherd 
1.Brienz 
2.Bernese Oberland
3.Lauterbrunnen
4.Lake Lungern
5.Rosenlaui
6.Gimmelwald
7.Mürren
8.Bernese Oberland
9.Wengen
10.Meiringen

node.text:
Beautiful in All seasons 🇨🇭
Autumn in Switzerland is the best time for hiking,strolling across 🌳 forests,and simply being outdoors.This photo set proves it!

Who can’t get enough of fall?🍂Share with us your favorite autumn destinations and activities below—we’re all ears 😍

📍Zürich,Switzerland 🇨🇭
📸 @sinhue_boksberger

node.text:
The breathtaking Valleys of Switzerland 🇨🇭with these gorgeous Towns and Mountains

These areas offer a variety of landscapes that make it perfect for all kinds of outdoor sports.

Swipe through and marvel at these incredible places! Bookmark this for reference for your future Switzerland Trip 📜🇨🇭
